@page
@model Roblox.Website.Pages.Auth.Privacy

@section MetaTags {
    <title>Privacy Policy – Shklurb</title>
}

<style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Segoe+UI:700,400|Tahoma:700,400');
    body { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e2f0ff 0%, #7ad0ff 100%); font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;}
    .aero-logo { margin: 36px auto 10px auto; display: block; width: 180px; max-width: 70vw; filter: drop-shadow(0 8px 12px #7ee8ff66); border-radius: 16px;}
    .main-aero-card { background: linear-gradient(120deg, #f7fdff 60%, #8feeff30 100%); border-radius: 20px; box-shadow: 0 10px 40px #6fc6fc29, 0 2px 8px #7cdeff30; padding: 30px 16px 22px 16px; max-width: 700px; width: 97vw; text-align: left; margin: 24px auto 18px auto;}
    .main-aero-card h2 { font-size: 1.7em; color: #066bb8; margin-bottom: 10px;}
    .main-aero-card p, .main-aero-card li { color: #216ba0; font-size: 1.03em; }
    .main-aero-card ul { padding-left: 24px; }
</style>

<img class="aero-logo" src="/UnsecuredContent/shklurb-logo.png" alt="Shklurb Logo">

<div class="main-aero-card">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>
        At Shklurb, your privacy matters. We go out of our way to minimize data collection and keep your info secure.
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li><b>Personal Info:</b> We do <u>not</u> require your real name, email, or other personal info. You only need a social media profile for application verification.</li>
        <li><b>IP Addresses:</b> Your IP is <b>hashed</b> and only stored temporarily when needed for security or abuse prevention. It's never linked directly to your account and is deleted after 24 hours (or sooner).</li>
        <li><b>VPNs:</b> VPN usage is encouraged. We do not block VPNs, and recommend them for extra privacy.</li>
        <li><b>Game Servers:</b> Our game servers never receive your real IP address, only a local proxy IP.</li>
        <li><b>Cookies:</b> We use cookies for login sessions only. No third-party tracking or ad cookies.</li>
        <li><b>Analytics:</b> We collect minimal usage stats (page visits, etc.) to improve the site—never personal or sensitive data.</li>
        <li><b>3rd Party Services:</b> We do not sell, share, or give your data to advertisers, marketers, or anyone else.</li>
        <li><b>Right to Removal:</b> You can request account deletion at any time and all associated data will be purged.</li>
    </ul>
    <p style="margin-top:20px;">
        If you have questions or want more details, <a href="/contact" style="color:#138adc">contact us here</a>.
    </p>
    <p style="font-size:0.92em;color:#5980a2;margin-top:18px;">Last updated: August 2025</p>
</div>
